/*The steps involved in establishing a socket on the client side are as follows
 *
 *1.Create a socket with the socket() system call
 *2.Connect the socket to the address of the server using the connect() system call
 *3.Send and receive data. Simply use read() and write() system calls
 *
 *Steps of establishing a socket on the server side
 *
 *1.Create a socket with socket() system call
 *2.Bind the socket to an address using bind()
 *3.Listen for connections with listen() system call
 *4.Accept a connection with accept() system call
 *5.Send and receive data
 *
 *
*/
